title: Toni Childs - The Videos - VHS Rip
description:
Here&#039;s a somewhat hard to find VHS tape from Toni Childs (1989).  It features three videos from her debut A&M release Union.  Dominic Sena directs the first one, "Don&#039;t Walk Away."  There&#039;s also a short interview with Toni at the end.

Quality is decent.  Video source was NTSC but, most of the video didn&#039;t appear telecined.  It ended up looking better to me after just de-interlacing and leaving the frame rate alone.  Audio is MP3.
